dated : [11/3/2015]

    we have trained a model with a given α on the train-set and test it on the validation-set and repeat this for the
    full range of possible α values in our grid.
    we have picked the best α value (i.e. the one that gives the lowest error)
    after finding the the value of α, we have retrain the new nodel with this value of alpha.

    
